{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-7","id":"msg_013qSLVjH5BvApzD3kXXAQHC","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01CZ1yjWNvE98eK2YSHPnDrg","name":"Bash","input":{"command":"git commit -m \"$(cat <<'EOF'\nRALPH: A.33 Auth-gated Get Pro pricing CTA (closes #33)\n\nWires the pricing Pro CTA to the auth state and Stripe checkout. Server\npages /, /pricing read the current user and pass isAuthed down through\nPricing to a new client ProCta component.\n\n- Logged out: ProCta renders an anchor to\n  /login?next={pathname+hash}&notice=signin (next composed at click time\n  from window.location, fallback href uses usePathname). After sign-in\n  the user lands back on the pricing surface they came from.\n- Logged in: ProCta renders a button that calls the shared\n  startCheckout helper with the cadence currently selected in the\n  toggle. Pending state flips the label to 'Redirecting…'; failures\n  render an inline alert.\n- New buildLoginNext(pathname, hash) helper composes the next param;\n  output round-trips through the existing sanitizeNext on /login.\n- Free plan CTA unchanged (still /download in both auth states).\n- No new server routes; existing checkout/webhook/portal untouched.\n\nFiles:\n  src/lib/auth/build-login-next.ts (new)\n  src/lib/auth/build-login-next.test.ts (new)\n  src/components/sections/pro-cta.tsx (new)\n  src/components/sections/pro-cta.test.tsx (new)\n  src/components/sections/pricing.tsx\n  src/components/sections/pricing.test.tsx\n  src/app/page.tsx\n  src/app/pricing/page.tsx\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.7 <noreply@anthropic.com>\nEOF\n)\"","description":"Commit changes"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":430,"cache_read_input_tokens":88832,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":430},"output_tokens":58,"service_tier":"standard","inference